t_Notes":"http://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/base-classes/oracle/mysteries/paizo---oracle-mysteries/dark-tapestry\r\n\r\n\r\nGift of Madness (Su): You tap into the unthinkable void between the stars and cause a single living creature within 30 feet to become confused for 1 round. A successful Will save negates the effect. This is a mind-affecting compulsion effect. At 7th level, the confusion lasts for a number of rounds equal to your oracle level. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your Charisma modifier.\r\n\r\nCloak of Darkness (Su): You conjure a cloak of shadowy darkness that grants you a +4 armor bonus and a +2 circumstance bonus on Stealth checks. At 7th level, and every four levels thereafter, these bonuses increase by +2. You can use this cloak for 1 hour per day per oracle level. The duration does not need to be consecutive, but it must be spent in 1-hour increments.\r\n\r\nPierce the Veil (Su): Your bond with the alien denizens of the Dark Tapestry allows you to see in even the deepest darkness. You gain darkvision 60 feet. At 11th level, you can see perfectly in darkness of any kind, even in absolute darkness or the darkness created by a deeper darkness spell.","__txt_note":null,"__txt_text":null,"__txt_text1":"","__txt_text2":"","__txt_text3":null,"__txt_text4":null,"__txt_text5":null,"__txt_text6":null,"__txt_text7":null,"__txt_text8":null,"__txt_text9":null,"__txt_text10":null,"__txt_text11":null,"__txt_text12":null,"__txt_text13":null,"__txt_text14":null,"__txt_text15":null,"__txt_d4p01desc":null,"__txt_d4p02desc":null,"__txt_d4p03desc":null,"__txt_d4p04desc":null,"__txt_d4p05desc":null,"__txt_d4p06desc":null,"__txt_d4p07desc":null,"__txt_d4p08desc":null,"__txt_d4p09desc":null,"__txt_d4p10desc":null,"__txt_d4p11desc":null,"__txt_d4p12desc":null,"__txt_d4p13desc":null,"__txt_d4p14desc":null,"__txt_d4p15desc":null,"__txt_d4p16desc":null,"__txt_d4p17desc":null,"__txt_d4p18desc":null,"__txt_d4p19desc":null,"__txt_d4p20desc":null